-- Japan Will Set Up Special Economic Zone to Promote Investment, Kan Says
-- B y   S a c h i k o   S a k a m a k i
-- 2010-11-13T00:46:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-13/japan-will-set-up-special-economic-zone-to-promote-investment-kan-says.html
Japan’s Prime Minister Naoto Kan
said his government will create a “special economic zone” to
promote investment.  Speaking to business executives on the sidelines of the
Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation forum in Yokohama, Japan, Kan
today also said his administration will compile an investment
plan this month.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sachiko Sakamaki in Tokyo at 
 ssakamaki1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
